* pop(): Removes and returns the top node from the stack (throws EmptyStackException if the stack is empty)
* peek(): Returns the top node from the stack (throws EmptyStackException if the stack is empty)
* isEmpty(): Returns true if the stack is empty, false otherwise
* size(): Returns the current size of the stack

